Package org.omg.dds.sub

Interface Subscriber.DataState

All Superinterfaces:
Cloneable, DDSObject
Enclosing interface:
Subscriber
public static interface Subscriber.DataState extends DDSObject, Cloneable
A DataState encapsulates sets of sample states, view states, and instance states as a convenience. Instances of DataState may be unmodifiable, in which case methods that would change them shall throw UnsupportedOperationException.
